<script>
import Layout from "@/layouts/main.vue";
import PageHeader from "@/components/page-header";
import CardHeader from "@/common/card-header";

export default{
    components: {
        Layout,
        PageHeader,
        CardHeader

    },
    data(){
        return{
            title: "Liste des contribuables",
            items: [
                {
                    text: "Tableau de bord",
                    href: "/",
                },
                {
                    text: "collectivités",
                    href: "/",
                },
                {
                    text: "contribuables",
                    active: true,
                },
            ],
        }
    }

}
</script>
<template>
    <Layout>
        <PageHeader :title="title" :items="items" />
        <b-row>
            <b-col xl="6">
                <b-card no-body>
                    <CardHeader title="Default Table" />
                </b-card>
            </b-col>
        </b-row>
    </Layout>
</template>
